<p>
  <span class="nym">Homobon</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>homo</i> 'man' + <span class="lang">Latin</span> <i>bonus</i> 'good'.
  </span>
  
</p>
  
<div class="usg">
  <p>The name of a 12th C Italian saint, the patron of tailors, shoemakers, clothworkers, and Cremona, Italy.</p>
</div>
  
  
<div class="def">
  <p>Cf. <a class="nym" href="Bonomo">Bonomo</a>.</p>
</div>
  


